comment.text: This has collided with the rebuild for GStreamer 1.24, which was built *first*, but because this update got pushed to *stable* after just one day, I need to rebuild qt6-qtmultimedia a second time. Please coordinate this better next time.
This unfortunately broke the GammaRay package because no build of it was included while it has a strict version dependency on it like some other packages included here.

long_desc.thetext: QAbstractOAuth in Qt Network Authorization in Qt before 5.15.17, 6.x before 6.2.13, 6.3.x through 6.5.x before 6.5.6, and 6.6.x through 6.7.x before 6.7.1 uses only the time to seed the PRNG, which may result in guessable values.

Affects: fedora-40 [bug 2282869]

http://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=2282852
